去年交付了 180 万辆汽车，因此此次召回占该公司年产量的 10% 以上。如果这听起来很熟悉，那么六周前，特斯拉因 Autopilot 功能出现严重安全问题而召回了超过 200 万辆汽车。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tesla-recalls-200000-vehicles-because-of-a-faulty-backup-camera-153302523.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-confirms-it-blocked-taylor-swift-searches-to-prioritize-safety-153136902.html">X 屏蔽了泰勒·斯威夫特的搜索以“安全优先”</a></h2><h3>上周，这位歌手的色情深度伪造品在网上疯传。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/x-confirms-it-blocked-taylor-swift-searches-to-prioritize-safety-153136902.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-01/f9651230-be91-11ee-addb-dfb4ae94f70e" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-01/f9651230-be91-11ee-addb-dfb4ae94f70e" style="height:429px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="10a9a0d7-ec92-3da8-87b2-951f716d0638"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">路透社/路透社</div></figure></a><p>X 证实，在泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的色情深度假货开始在平台上流传后，它正在阻止用户搜索泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的名字。该网站的访问者从周六开始注意到，一些包含斯威夫特名字的搜索只会返回一条错误消息。</p><p>该平台对该问题的处理一直很缓慢。上周三这些图片疯传后，斯威夫特们把事情掌握在自己手中（当然！），他们大规模举报了分享这些图片的账户，并在与这位歌手相关的主题标签上充斥着积极的内容。你不记得<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2017-08-25-taylor-swift-kanye-west-solange-vanish-from-instagram-and-twitter.html">蛇表情符号传奇</a>吗？</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-confirms-it-blocked-taylor-swift-searches-to-prioritize-safety-153136902.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/x-confirms-it-blocked-taylor-swift-searches-to-prioritize-safety-153136902.html"><br><br></a> <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/engadget-podcast-the-mac-turns-40-141509644.html">Engadget 播客：Mac 迎来 40 岁生日</a></h2><h3>我们回顾了 Framework Laptop 16。</h3><h3></h3><p>本周关于 Mac 步入中年、能够玩游戏的模块化笔记本电脑以及苹果汽车梦想依然存在的想法、感受和事实。本周，新闻编辑内森·英格拉汉姆 (Nathan Ingraham) 也加入了德文德拉 (Devindra) 的行列。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/engadget-podcast-the-mac-turns-40-141509644.html"><strong>听这里。</strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-that-ai- generated-george-carlin-comedy-special-was-writing-by- humans-121501471.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-that-ai-generated-george-carlin-comedy-special-was-written-by-humans-121501471.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 43ee7d8a-67ed-462a-a9ad-fbea0f3778c9 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mat Smith]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 29 Jan 2024 12:15:01 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1706525850</ingested><modified> 2024-01-29T10:57:37+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Celebrities]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="928" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2F5a6c5700-bc71-11ee-aeff-41fd352cacc9&amp;resize=1400%2C928&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=f6f43cc88e318efcca60734379a2b8d9f2edb579" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="928"